    "sustainable growth": "持続可能な成長",
    "shareholder value": "株主価値"
  }
}

{
  "tone_feedback": "The text uses polite form and is clear. Consider replacing "取り組んでいます" with the more formal "尽力しております" to increase formality. No slang detected."
